OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776085870
OL,3,CCoventry City's promotion party has
OL,4,Cbeen paused... at least until next week
OL,6,FIt was a rare afternoon to forget for
OL,7,FCoventry City in what has otherwise
OL,8,Fbeen a season for the history books.
OL,10,FThe stands were packed at the CBS
OL,11,FArena, a sold out crowd were ready to
OL,12,Fwitness destiny.
OL,14,FInstead, they were treated to a
OL,15,Fstubborn stalemate that proved the
OL,16,Ffinal steps of a marathon are often
OL,17,Fthe hardest to take.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
