OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776085870
OL,3,CCoventry City's promotion party has
OL,4,Cbeen paused... at least until next week
OL,6,FOn paper, the two teams couldn't be
OL,7,Fmore far apart. Sheffield Wednesday
OL,8,Fare rooted to the bottom of the table,
OL,9,Fand enduring one of the darkest
OL,10,Fchapters in their clubs history.
OL,11,FWhereas Coventry are charging towards
OL,12,Fthe Premier League at full steam, a
OL,13,Fsky blue tidal wave that have swept
OL,14,Fnearly every team aside this year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776085870
OL,3,CCoventry City's promotion party has
OL,4,Cbeen paused... at least until next week
OL,6,FFor the second time this week the
OL,7,FCoventry faithful were treated to a
OL,8,Fgoalless draw. But this one, stung
OL,9,Fmore. Not just because of the
OL,10,Foccasion, but also because of the
OL,11,Fopposition. Sheffield Wednesday
OL,12,Farrived at the CBS Arena having lost
OL,13,F30 out of 41 games this season.
OL,15,FIn the match itself, Coventry were
OL,16,Ftreated to many chances - but failed
OL,17,Fto put any away. Big chances from
OL,18,FEllis Simms, and an overhead kick at
OL,19,Fthe death, but the ball would not
OL,20,Fcross the line.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776085870
OL,3,CCoventry City's promotion party has
OL,4,Cbeen paused... at least until next week
OL,6,FFans we spoke to at the stadium,
OL,7,Fwhilst stung by the result, can't help
OL,8,Fbut take in perspective. One fan said
OL,9,F"It's never easy but it's another
OL,10,Fpoint. We didn't lose today. We'll
OL,11,Fhave to do it at Blackburn next week!".
OL,13,FThat would sow it up, a win in
OL,14,FLancashire and Coventry are officially
OL,15,Funcatchable mathematically seeing them
OL,16,Freturn to the top flight regardless of
OL,17,Fteams or results elsewhere.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
