OL,3,CCoventry City's promotion party has
OL,4,Cbeen paused... at least until next week
OL,6,FThe 25 year wait for Premier League
OL,7,Ffootball is agonisingly close to being
OL,8,Fover. The champagne is on ice, and the
OL,9,FSky Blue banners are still in the
OL,10,Fgarage. But of course in the grand
OL,11,Fscheme of things, and having waited so
OL,12,Flong, what's a few days for Coventry
OL,13,Ffans?
OL,15,FWant more on Coventry City, head to
OL,16,FITVX to watch 'Coventry City: The
OL,17,FResurrection', featuring exclusive
OL,18,Fclips from Frank Lampard
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
